{"tid":743373,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點防止昆蟲入屋","createTime":"2018-07-15T11:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T04:00:12.000Z","uid":9153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"988a28d4ddbce98223cf11d4dd79ec8540b7ad14","tid":743373,"uid":9153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"屋企有隻貓<br />\n本身已經唔會開窗<br />\n夏天日頭長開冷氣<br />\n但呢排翻風落雨<br />\n同一棟又有好多單位裝修<br />\n搞到D小昆蟲成日入屋 (已經成日係渠口噴殺蟲水/已經痴左膠條塞大門條空隙)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bugscare.com/product/10.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bugscare.com%2Fproduct%2F10.html&d=y1ExX8AUYFFJkpHQSQ5RNbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8d64ae16\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bugscare.com/product/10.html</a><br />\n之前見實惠有呢隻驅蟲大王脈沖版<br />\n會唔會對屋企隻貓有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又或者有無方法可以防止入屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb4325e91aed2c560fb0a64fc13ef0264649a21","tid":743373,"uid":9153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T18:15:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f9ec928f886bbe35b0f2496359ce3930004f082","tid":743373,"uid":9153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:00:12.000Z","msg":"推"}]}